Name: Starfighter Arduxim
About the game: Strap into the cockpit of your Arduxim fighter and take on enemy starships in this first-person tactical space shooter. Navigate through dangerous ice crystal fields, take hyper gates to other systems, take on enormous capital ships and more. Includes: A fourteen mission story based campaign covering your first tour of duty on the front lines Multiplayer to test your skills against other pilots and AI bots Survival/horde challenge mode with online leader board Tutorial Practice mode Starfighter Arduxim requires motion controllers, a gamepad, joystick or HOTAS. Controls are fully customisable.
